[    1.132544] context-{2:2}
[    1.132545] 1 lock held by swapper/0/0:
[    1.132547]  #0: ffffffffa010c4c0 (rcu_read_lock){....}-{1:3}, at: vmbus_chan_sched+0x31/0x2b0
